{"tid":1419960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家幾時先可以將帶gear變成習慣","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:31:54.000Z","uid":14680,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5e26657827733f4ad0d642433821d0a7ae25e68c","tid":1419960,"uid":14680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:11:30.000Z","msg":"前線唔洗講，和理非們<br />\n你地唔係真係認為你地和理非，班狗就會跟住和理非下話？<br />\n近來既所有集會<br />\n就算有哂不反對通知書都好<br />\n每一個都一定會係催淚彈、甚至橡膠子彈收場<br />\n點解尋日出去可以見到接近8 成人都係冇gear<br />\n得個普通口罩？<br />\n又或者仲係用緊最最基本既新手裝：透到氣既眼罩、N95加保鮮紙？<br />\n變左其實敢行上前既人真係好少<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為和理非企後面就冇事<br />\n煙隨風飄散，後面一樣會中招<br />\n亦唔好覺得自己當刻冇乜大礙就冇問題<br />\n而家你地吸入去既係過期催淚彈<br />\n後遺症可以係好嚴重！<br />\n<br />\n如果冇錢買，我相信你地出聲，大把有能力既人會幫你<br />\n如果怕俾狗逗，當全部人都有gear係身時<br />\n狗逗你都冇意思！！<br />\n<br />\n就算唔講生理上受唔受傷<br />\n當你有充夠既gear時，心理上你都會大膽左<br />\n大家一齊有gear咁行前啲，同前線齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n所以求求大家<br />\n最低限制有泳鏡/不透氣眼罩<br />\n同埋最最簡單既3200！<br />\n就算真係唔洗用到，袋定係袋度真係唔會浪費你好多位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd32aeb061ec9c3fd14f14c3ac4822158cf3bd7","tid":1419960,"uid":259700,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bd8dd178eae03d50ded204a04b24bdbb1481520","tid":1419960,"uid":60434,"